Goals are:
* Reducing vulnerability to climate change impacts of people and tourism sector, in particular the most
* Shifting towards a green development path by promoting low-carbon development and technologies;

(2008) adapted fours guiding principles from UNDP adaption framework that are highly relevant for tourism.
* Place adaptation in a development context;
* Build on current adaptive experience to cope with future climate variability;
* Recognise that adaptation occurs at different levels in particular, at the local level; and
* Recognise that adaptation is an ongoing process.
